&lt;p&gt;We’re hiring a driven and consultative SMB Account Executive to help accelerate Lattice’s next phase of growth. This is an opportunity for ambitious sales professionals who thrive in fast-paced environments, excel in high-velocity sales cycles, and are energised by building strong customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
