&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full sales cycle from prospecting through close for SMB organisations, delivering a high-quality customer experience throughout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistently meet or exceed monthly and quarterly new business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate pipeline through proactive outbound prospecting, which represents a critical driver of success in the role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a healthy, disciplined pipeline through strong follow-up, deal management, and forecasting hygiene.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead thoughtful discovery conversations to uncover business-level challenges and goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position Lattice’s solutions through a consultative sales approach tailored to each customer’s needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a strong understanding of the HR technology landscape, industry trends, and Lattice’s competitive positioning to guide customers through the buying process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Account Managers to cross-sell new services into our existing customer base.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute positively to team culture through collaboration, curiosity, accountability, and an eagerness to learn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
