&lt;li&gt;Exceptional verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A high sense of ownership and accountability - you proactively manage your business and don’t require close oversight to maintain momentum.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An experimental mindset and eagerness to leverage AI and modern sales tools to work smarter, move faster, and improve execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High coachability, intellectual curiosity, and a genuine desire to continually hone your craft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for Lattice’s mission and alignment with our values: Ship Shipmate Self, Clear Eyes, Own the Outcome, and What’s Next?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re excited by the opportunity to help organisations “make work meaningful” and you’re a proactive, results-driven sales professional ready to make a significant impact, we’d love to hear from you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
